adaf5e4b-b539-474e-9073-f343913cf4ea.name: Count of Windows VM
adaf5e4b-b539-474e-9073-f343913cf4ea.formula: count(${adaptertype=VMWARE, objecttype=VirtualMachine, attribute=summary|guest|fullName, depth=5, where ="summary|guest|fullName startsWith Microsoft Windows"})

9f82b1e0-ffeb-424f-bbdd-16fbc0fce609.name: Count of non-Windows VM
9f82b1e0-ffeb-424f-bbdd-16fbc0fce609.formula: count(${adaptertype=VMWARE, objecttype=VirtualMachine, attribute=summary|guest|fullName, depth=5, where ="summary|guest|fullName !startsWith Microsoft Windows"})
